It feels nice to drive on the route

7
00:02:33,601 --> 00:02:34,904
Sakura told me about.

8
00:02:35,706 --> 00:02:37,126
Let's see.

9
00:02:37,127 --> 00:02:38,798
I came from the Western Line

10
00:02:38,799 --> 00:02:41,705
and passed through the Mount Kayagatake
Broad Area Agriculture Line.

11
00:02:42,499 --> 00:02:45,299
