00:11:20,700 --> 00:11:23,194
From there, take the Shirai Koshu Line,

151
00:11:23,195 --> 00:11:24,511
Miyasaka Road,

152
00:11:24,512 --> 00:11:27,011
Kanegawa Broad Area Agriculture Line.

153
00:11:27,012 --> 00:11:31,006
That makes one complete lap
around the Kofu Basin.

154
00:11:31,007 --> 00:11:33,610
It feels like overlooking
the surroundings of a basin.

155
00:11:33,611 --> 00:11:35,204
Given it's a complete circle,

156
00:11:35,205 --> 00:11:37,502
it kind of reminds me
of taking a tour around a volcano.

