161
00:12:04,700 --> 00:12:06,710
you'll see even more places lighting up.

162
00:12:08,997 --> 00:12:09,893
Well then,

163
00:12:09,894 --> 00:12:12,607
let's pull over and take a good look.

164
00:12:15,903 --> 00:12:17,612
I remember now.

165
00:12:29,199 --> 00:12:31,386
This was the road

166
00:12:31,387 --> 00:12:33,012
