167
00:12:41,497 --> 00:12:44,694
There seems to be
a light show here at night.

168
00:12:44,695 --> 00:12:46,398
Really?

169
00:12:46,994 --> 00:12:49,002
Should we come again at night?

170
00:12:49,596 --> 00:12:51,107
If it's not very crowded.

171
00:12:52,403 --> 00:12:54,710
Sakura! Take a picture for me!

172
00:12:58,200 --> 00:13:00,606
