337
00:23:36,293 --> 00:23:36,941
WHEN ENJOYING CAMPING,
BE SURE TO FOLLOW THE RULES

338
00:23:36,942 --> 00:23:37,589
OF THE CAMPGROUND AND ITS FACILITIES.

339
00:23:37,590 --> 00:23:38,697
DON'T FORGET TO PUT OUT YOUR CAMPFIRE
